<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>HELP</title>
    <%- include('./partials/head') %> 
    <%- include('./partials/navbar-test') %>
</head>
<body class="pt-5 mt-4" style="height: 2000px; font-family: Open Sans;">
    <div id="carouselExampleSlidesOnly" class="carousel mx-0" data-bs-ride="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-inner">
          <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img src="assets/SeaJacket.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
            <div class="carousel-caption d-block" style="top: 60%;">
                <h1 style="font-size: 50px;">Help</h1>
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-10 col-md-8 mt-5">
            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-10 col-md-8" style="font-size: 16;">
                    
                    <div class="row justify-content-center">
                        <div class="col d-flex justify-content-center my-5" style="font-size: 25px;">
                            <b>Related Actions</b>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="row d-flex justify-content-between mb-5 mt-4">
                        <div class="col-6 col-sm-5">
                            <div class="container" style="background-color: gray;border-radius: 15px; min-height: 70px;min-width:60px ;">
                                <b>My orders</b>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-6 col-sm-5">
                            <div class="container" style="background-color: gray;border-radius: 15px;  min-height: 70px; min-width:60px ;">
                                <b>Send us an email</b>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col">
                            <div class="container justify-content-center" data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseQ1" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseExample">
                                <b>How do I pick up my order?</b> 
                            </div>
                            <div class="collapse" id="collapseQ1">
                                <div class="card card-body">
                                    Once you have received a confirmation email for your order, it will be available for pick up when shown to the receptionist at the main office. 
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <hr>

                            <div class="container justify-content-center" data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseQ2" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseExample">
                                <b>What should I do if my order is late?</b> 
                            </div>
                            <div class="collapse" id="collapseQ2">
                                <div class="card card-body">
                                    If you haven’t received a confirmation email for your order after the expected date, you can send us an email at (), or talk to the receptionist at the main office. 
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <hr>

                            <div class="container justify-content-center" data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseQ3" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseExample">
                                <b>How do I cancel my order?</b> 
                            </div>
                            <div class="collapse" id="collapseQ3">
                                <div class="card card-body">
                                    An order can be cancelled any time before the end of the “cancellation period” through the “My Orders” page.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <hr>

                            <div class="container justify-content-center" data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseQ4" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseExample">
                                <b>How do I return my past order?</b> 
                            </div>
                            <div class="collapse" id="collapseQ4">
                                <div class="card card-body">
                                    Unfortunately we do not accept any returns of previous orders.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    
                </div>
        
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
